    An enumeration of possible statuses for an AbstractCertificationItem.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      Challenged
      The certification item has been challenged.
      Complete
      The certification item has been fully acted upon.
      Delegated
      The certification item has been delegated.
      Open
      The certification item has not been acted upon.
      Returned
      The certification item has been returned ("bounced back") from a delegate that has chosen not to work on the item.
      WaitingReview
      The certification item was completed by a delegate, but has not yet been reviewed by the owner.
